hopobject.body: Where's the postbox? owl pharmacy california The 'Don't Think They Know' singer has been on felony probation in the 2009 beating of former girlfriend Rihanna and has been in and out of court since the assault, making reports on fulfilling the requirements of his probation. Brown, who reportedly crashed his Porshe in February 2013 as well as had a fight in the same month with Frank Ocean, has tweeted his 12.8 million Twitter followers to try to explain: "I did everything I was suppose to do during the so called hit n run, I provided the correct info. There were no injuries or damages. C'mon!!"
